SIMPLE: luckless
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Luckless
<hw>Luck"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Being without luck; unpropitious;
unfortunate; unlucky; meeting with ill success or bad fortune; <as>as, a
<ex>luckless</ex> gamester; a <ex>luckless</ex> maid.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Prayers made and granted in a <qex>luckless</qex> hour.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Luck"less*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Lock"less*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lucknow</ent>⟦br⟧
